This is such a gorgeous kitchen! The before pictures are unbelievable! ✨ I'm offering a special for virtual consults for $60 for 1 room, $115 for 2 rooms, $165 for 3 rooms, $210 for 4 rooms & $40 for each additional room. A combination room such as living/dining is $100 if you want help with both. Do you need design direction and advice... but you want to do the shopping on your own to save money?  Do you need help decorating your home?  Are you overwhelmed or not sure how to take the next step? 
I spend time getting to know you, your space & the style you would like to achieve.  I can help you arrange your current furniture, 
update your space, select new paint, or any area that you feel stuck. 
We will chat over FaceTime or WhatsApp and you can show me your home. After our consult I'll also send visual examples of items we discussed.  I empower you so that I you feel confident to implement the changes on your own and save money!  I’ll give you direction and help you make choices while you shop. 
If you want me to shop for items for you I charge $60 an hour. I’ll send you links to purchase items online at whatever stores you chose to shop. (Target, TJMaxx, Wayfair, Pottery Barn, etc) 
To schedule a consult just send a DM or email. Let me know what days and times work best for your schedule and what time zone you are in.
Click on the link in my bio to see my website or @deirdres_design.home.  USA & Canada only
